    "The study also showed that AI tailors products, services, and marketing to customers' tastes.",
    "However, using AI to improve user experience has drawbacks.",
    "AI-driven personalization, chatbots, and virtual assistants profoundly impact consumer experience in numerous business sectors.",
    "AI has improved customer satisfaction and loyalty by gathering and analyzing consumer data to tailor products and services.",
    "In retail, AIpowered personalized recommendations have increased sales and revenue."
